body:
SEWA RUMAH di Puchong - APARTMENT KEKWA, PUTRA PERDANA

Harga Sewa Bulanan: RM 900
Deposit Rumah: 2+1
Deposit Api & Air: RM 300

Lokasi strategik di Puchong, Apartment Kekwa di Putra Perdana menawarkan kemudahan dan keselesaan untuk anda!
Apartment ini terletak berhampiran dengan pelbagai kemudahan utama, termasuk:

Sekolah: Berdekatan dengan SK Taman Putra Perdana, SMK Putra Perdana, dan Sekolah Rendah Agama Putra Perdana, sangat sesuai untuk keluarga dengan anak-anak sekolah.

Lebuh Raya: Akses mudah ke Lebuhraya Maju (MEX), memudahkan perjalanan ke Kuala Lumpur, Putrajaya, Cyberjaya, dan KLIA.

Kedai Runcit & Pasaraya: Hanya beberapa minit dari Pasaraya Lotus dan banyak kedai runcit berdekatan untuk keperluan harian anda. Lotus's Bandar Bukit Puchong hanya mengambil masa 10 hingga 15 minit perjalanan dengan kereta.

Stesen Polis: Balai Polis Putra Perdana yang berdekatan menjamin keselamatan kawasan ini.

Pengangkutan Awam: Hentian bas hanya berhadapan dengan apartment, dengan laluan untuk bas percuma SMART SELANGOR yang memudahkan mobiliti anda.

Kemudahan Kesihatan: Terdapat beberapa klinik kesihatan berdekatan, termasuk Klinik Putra Perdana, Klinik Siti, dan Klinik Hentian, yang menawarkan perkhidmatan perubatan harian dan kecemasan.

Ruang di dalam rumah: Luas, mempunya balkoni di ruang tamu.

the Golden Triangle of Kuala Lumpur City Centre,
surrounded by numerous highways such as AKLEH,
DUKE and MRR2 and major roads such as Jalan Ampang
enables us to skip jams at all time. What's more
its values are further accentuated with this high
accessibility to the development makes our
condominium the perfect place meant to stay or to
invest.

By using MRR2, it is almost accessible to any area
in Kuala Lumpur with AKLEH Highway; it takes 5
minutes drive to KLCC whereas through DUKE
Highway, it takes 15 minutes to reach Damansara
and 10 minutes to enter North South Expressway
(PLUS). Not to be missed the major roads such as
Jalan Ampang leads to most of the Embassies in
Kuala Lumpur City Centre.

The condominium project benefits from a good
catchment area as well, given its proximity to a
myriad of facilities in the area the Sayfol
International School, Ampang Point, Cold Storage,
Ampang Puteri Specialists Centre, Gleneagles Intan
Medical Centre and more, 3 storeys Roof Parking
and open space parking at D'Suria Condominium is
designed to serve the best interest to the
residents in terms of security and conveniences.

body:
Mont Kiara Pines unit for rent:
-1200sf
-fully furnished
-low floor.
-well kept and renovated unit
-Must view!

Facilities:
-Barbecue area
-Salon
-Squash court
-Covered car park
-Badminton
-Gymnasium
-Tennis court
-Swimming pool
-Playground
-Mini market
-Sauna
-Jogging track

Mont Kiara Pines, Mont Kiara
Mont Kiara Pines is one of the pioneer residential developments in Mont Kiara enclave. It is more than a decade old and developed by renowned Sunrise. It comprises of 3 block towers which namely Aspen, Everett and Scott.

Mont Kiara Pines is located next to Mont Kiara Palma, One Mont Kiara, i-Zen Kiara I, and i-Zen Kiara II. Besides that, it is one of the most strategic located residential in Mont Kiara as it is located within walking distance to Plaza Mont Kiara and Mont Kiara International School.

Mont Kiara Pines is easily accessible from various main roads and highways as well as nearby numerous prime areas. You can utilize NKVE, Penchala Link, Jalan Duta, Jalan Kuching and SPRINT highway to access Kuala Lumpur city centre, Petaling Jaya, Taman Tun Dr Ismail and Bangsar within minutes of driving. It takes around 20 minutes to reach the city centre and 10 minutes to reach Damansara Heights.

Mont Kiara Pines is within walking distance to Plaza Mont Kiara, which famous as a chilling place to hang out with family and friends. It is also near to Mont Kiara International School, which the kids can just take a walk to the school. If you are a golf enthusiast, take your club bag and hit the green at KGPA, KLGC, Tropicana Golf and Country Resort, and Sri Selangor Golf Club which are not far from the area.
